Elite-2-Controller-Black-Xbox-One/dp/B07SFKTLZM?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">售价 140 美元</a>）等替代品提供了更广泛的功能，但如果您只需要基本功能，标准 Xbox 控制器应该可以满足您的需求。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>主要的障碍是它仍然依赖 AA 电池供电。这使它比 DualSense 的续航时间更长，但如果您不想定期更换电池，则必须购买<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Microsoft;elmt:;cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=67071605-d4df-494e-8d9c-c9c236b8bb38&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Microsoft&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaYhXGUQfs2fL_NJaww321wHNmtmBwCSlv2STdXcDzKK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fd%2Fxbox-rechargeable-battery-usb-c-cable-latest-model%2F8thsbp49z46x" class="rapid-with-clickid">单独的可充电电池组</a>。不过，如果您能忍受这种麻烦，那么您可以通过购买一对可充电 AA（例如<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9QYW5hc29uaWMtQkstM01DQ0E4QkEtZW5lbG9vcC1QcmUtQ2hhcmdlZC1SZWNoYXJnZWFibGUvZHAvQjAwSkhLU01KVS8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXVwLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJmNWIxMTM4OC0xYTEzLTQxN2QtOWFiNS02NWVmZmE5N2ZiNTMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAat3yeyq5WaW_GTheSomu3zcXEMX18py7zYCfeIgd90a&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPanasonic-BK-3MCCA8BA-eneloop-Pre-Charged-Rechargeable%2Fdp%2FB00JHKSMJU%2F" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Panasonic-BK-3MCCA8BA-eneloop-Pre-Charged-Rechargeable/dp/B00JHKSMJU/?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Panasonic Eneloops）</a>来减少购买新电池的需要。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=e